"<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Give the gift of creativity! Our DIY "
"Workshop Gift Card lets your loved ones choose a sewing class that suits "
"their style and schedule; whether they're beginners or seasoned makers. A "
"unique, hands-on experience they'll remember (and wear)!</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">贈送一份充滿創意的禮物！我們的 DIY 工作坊禮"
"品卡，讓你的親朋好友可以根據自己的風格及日程安排，選擇合適的縫紉課程，無論他"
"們是初學者抑或經驗豐富的工匠。這是一次獨特的手作體驗，會讓學員難忘（並樂於穿"
"戴自己的作品）！</span>"

